I also have a bracelet of fortitude (12ac 15sta and 6 all Svs). Not using it right now as I haven't hit the ac softcap.<br>
I think my dex is a lil low (120dex when using ToD) so would like to keep it up.<br>
<br>
I have about 12k pp banked. Thoughts:<br>
<br>
1. Keep the cash and wait until level 60, prices will fall?<br>
<br>
2. Upgrade a 1hs (but I don't see anything relevant at that price range).<br>
<br>
3. Get a new cloak: Cloak of maelstrom for sta/hps and dex for procs - but lose some ac)?<br>
<br>
4. Attempt for Brellium cultural legs or BP (got a friend that does if for free if I have the components) - I got lucky on the pauldrons/boots/bracer (3 items in 4 attempts), but risking complete failure on legs/BP would hurt me bad.<br>
<br>
5. Try to get a Thurg/SS MQ legs? Note that quest legs are defaulted to clerics in my guild (for the AoE heal).<br>
<br>
6. Stop bothering fellow warriors and get bac to RL work?<br>
<br>
8. Get Shrunken goblin earring for insta click effect and atk buff? An enduring breath item (or just quest one in the grey?)?<br>
<br>
9. Better earring  than cougar claws?<br>
<br>
10. Any other ideas?<br>
<br>
